styles: .cookie-law .cookie-law-wrapper {  background: #333;  color: #bbb;  display: block;  font-family: Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;  font-size: 15px;  font-weight: 200;  line-height: 20px;  position: fixed;  bottom: 0;  left: 0;  width: 100%;  z-index: 999999999;  font-smooth: always;  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;}.cookie-law .cookie-law-wrapper a {  color: #bbb;  -webkit-transition: color .2s;  transition: color .2s;}.cookie-law .cookie-law-wrapper a:hover {  color: #fff;}.cookie-law .cookie-law-wrapper a:hover svg {  fill: #fff;}.cookie-law .cookie-law-wrapper .dismiss {  display: block;  box-sizing: border-box;  padding: 10px;  position: absolute;  top: 0;  right: 10px;  text-decoration: none;  line-height: 20px;}.cookie-law .cookie-law-wrapper .dismiss svg {  display: block;  fill: #bbb;  width: 20px;  height: 20px;  -webkit-transition: fill .2s;  transition: fill .2s;}.cookie-law .cookie-law-wrapper .copy {  box-sizing: border-box;  padding: 10px 60px 10px 10px;}.cookie-law .cookie-law-wrapper .copy span {  color: #fff;  font-weight: 400;}.cookie-law .cookie-law-wrapper .copy a {  text-decoration: underline;}.cookie-law .cookie-law-wrapper .copy a:active, .copy a:hover {    outline: 0;}@media (min-width: 600px) {  /* For bigger devices: */  .cookie-law .cookie-law-wrapper .copy {    padding: 20px 60px 20px 20px;    font-size: 18px;    line-height: 24px;  }  .cookie-law .cookie-law-wrapper .dismiss {    top: 10px;    right: 15px;  }  .cookie-law .cookie-law-wrapper .dismiss svg {    width: 24px;    height: 24px;  }}
arguments.template: By continuing to browse the site, you're agreeing to our use of cookies. Learn more in our privacy policy.
